Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:20.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}ずっと前から　決まっていたような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:26.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}遠い昔からわかってたような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:32.01,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}見えない線の上を辿るように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:37.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}導かれて愛　交差する世と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:43.69,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}背中合わせの光と影のように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:49.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}強く引かれるDestin Histoireを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:55.04,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}耳元でささやき呼ぶ声に振り向けば
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:01:00.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}気づかぬ　千切れていた扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:06.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}すこしの偶然と必然を繋ぐように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:12.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}動き始めた二つの椅子と
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:24.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}ずっと果てなく続いてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:20.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}仿佛早已注定一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:26.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}仿佛从遥远往昔就已彼此知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:32.01,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}仿佛顺着无形的红线在追寻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:37.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}那被引导的爱 和这交错的世间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:43.69,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}如同那背对背的光与影一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:49.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}又仿佛是强烈互相吸引的命运和历史
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:55.04,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}寻着耳畔的呼唤声转身望去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:01:00.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}不意之间 门扉已支离破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.94,0:01:06.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}就如同小小的偶然和必然有着密不可分的联系一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:12.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}与开始移动的席位一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:24.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}永远无止境地持续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.14,0:23:13.84,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}強く降り止まぬ雨に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.87,0:23:17.97,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}笑顔を忘れたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.03,0:23:22.68,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}苦しみすれ違う世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:30.20,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}争いと偽りの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:37.10,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}心枯らすのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.15,0:23:44.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}荒れ狂う波に　浮かぶ花のように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:51.78,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}never away 嵐も乗り越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.82,0:23:59.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}涸れ行く大地を苦しめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.20,0:24:10.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}go ahead まっすく歩み出せる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.10,0:23:13.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}永不停歇的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:17.93,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}让我忘记了欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:22.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}在困苦交织的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.67,0:23:30.16,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}充满了纠纷和虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.19,0:23:37.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}人心干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:44.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}仿佛是在狂暴的波涛中飘浮的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.37,0:23:51.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}never away 乘风破浪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:59.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}仿佛是折磨着这日渐干涸的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.16,0:24:10.27,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\blur1}go ahead 毫无迷惘地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:48.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lonely night fighting back again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:52.41,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,seems to be like it never ends
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:53.62,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,give us hope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:23:00.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,through the love feels for shined on way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:48.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独长夜 再次袭来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:52.41,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛它从未终结过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:53.62,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请通过爱赐予我们希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:23:00.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这暗夜中为我们照亮前进之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:01:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:55.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆里有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然…是书了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了把树叶隐藏在树林里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才来到了这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:09.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女在捡起书的时候 已经察觉到被你发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想到要藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说来 图书馆是最佳的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道那是什么书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎样才能找到呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道「通往天国的第十三阶台阶」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说要是停在那台阶的话 灵魂会被拖入那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一层收藏了古今中外的有关宗教学的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是天国的书架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 5…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.69,0:02:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6 7 8 9
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10 11 12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.33,0:03:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是「天国的第十三阶台阶」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算停在这里也安然无恙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女把书藏在了这层阶梯的书架上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「智慧之泉」是这样告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000008&\fs24\pos(425,372)}栖息于废仓库的迷之幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次轻描淡写的解决了谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「金色的妖精」「灰狼」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人感到不可思议的维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「在高塔居住的金色妖精」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的…妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 翻页太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.87,0:03:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的大头挡住我视线了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不能一起看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.22,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.02,0:04:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一个年代久远的异国传说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屹立于丛林深处的高塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住着一位金色的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道世上所有的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为困窘的人们指明道路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 作为代价 她会向对方索取灵魂来交换
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其灵魂吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得像是在描述维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然「图书馆里的金色妖精」指的是维多利加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.97,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明信片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇儿·布莱德利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是给艾薇儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄出人是布莱德利伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是艾薇儿的爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮票上没有邮戳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说信还没有交到艾薇儿手上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也没事了吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说腻了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为和她的关系变好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件的谜团应该解决了才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 骑士木乃伊事件才刚刚解决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又收到了怪盗潜入了这里村庄的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在搜寻他的踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是「怪盗奎亚那」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.61,0:05:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是横行了欧洲大陆的有名盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是在七 八年前就销声匿迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家传言说他隐退了或者是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 第二代的怪盗重现于世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们收到消息说他正前往这个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢 警官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得你给我的感觉和平常有点不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和维多利加一起的时候 你总是让我觉得很做作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括对我也是 整天的说「噢 小男孩」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 看到可疑人物就立刻通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学在仓库附近昏倒了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现了你 让花匠把你背了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那个仓库会出现女孩的幽灵 所以没人敢靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学不会是被幽灵袭击了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:08:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是艾薇儿袭击了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个怪谈多多的学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是藏着那本书的人是艾薇儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆里也有怪谈呢 我记得是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「金色的妖精」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个妖精头脑非常聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然什么问题都能解决 但代价是夺取人类的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.11,0:08:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是妖精 感觉更像是恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在图书馆最上层的 是维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直翘课 一个人看书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆里的不是金色的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个有着金发的小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她收取的东西也不是灵魂 是零食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是传言没人见过那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加是真实存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书…书…书…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 已经没事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 昨天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你听说了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.44,0:09:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个木乃伊 听说是学校的毕业生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想起来又…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本书你是在哪里捡到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被丢在花坛后边来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被丢掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是艾薇儿啊…那是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 好像会有幽灵出没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.42,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师把眼镜摘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有幽灵出现也完全看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…这样很危险 所以还是戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有也是幽灵 或是老头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是金色的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是女孩子呆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才明明在这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我只是想看看植物园
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪儿去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 并没人见过那个女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.55,0:11:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个吵闹的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给我带来打发无聊的东西了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被某人袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盗奎亚那的第二代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓库的幽灵什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我吃够苦头了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错 因为是零食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明长一副狗屎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫花林糖啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}花林糖：日本传统点心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 维多利加…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪盗 仓库的幽灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.91,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有图书馆的金色妖精吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里看上去不像是女孩子呆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有也是幽灵 或是老头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更像是金色的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫艾薇儿的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是第二代奎亚那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾 艾薇儿是第二代奎亚那？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是个吵闹的男生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那个 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把由智慧之泉重组的混沌碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所构成的事实告之于你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代奎亚那的真面目其实是马克·希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.37,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克·希姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代奎亚那在七 八年前突然销声匿迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而马克·希姆遭到谋杀是在八年前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是单纯的偶然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克·希姆…哦不 是奎亚那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必每年春天都把赃物藏匿到学校来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那本书也是其中之一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在藏好之前他就被困在了停尸房里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 艾薇儿也在找着那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇儿也在找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.86,0:13:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在一瞬间结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要开始无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓库的幽灵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说幽灵向你们诉说着什么是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 它喊着 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去救她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救幽灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓库里的幽灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才是真正的艾薇儿·布莱德利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.43,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我带来这种地方你到底有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得刚刚幽灵的声音好像是从这边发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是艾薇儿·布莱德利？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人乔装成我的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我搭上从英国开往苏瓦尔的火车时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们结识了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道这座学校里藏着爷爷留给我的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是瞄准了那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官 艾薇儿就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 给我藏到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 久城同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奎亚那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子是暴露了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:16:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我就是第二代奎亚那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说第一代变成木乃伊登场时 我也是吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 也是因此 我找到了那本书
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底把那个藏到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我打晕 把书丢掉的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是当时你手上也只有书而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色便士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.93,0:16:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张明信片到底在哪？！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明信片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你没注意到吗 名侦探同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色便士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是世界最早的邮票
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且更珍贵的是其中有几张因为印刷错误而价值连城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那张明信片？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的那个女孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.64,0:16:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为东西在她手上所以才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她完全不存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来这种地方就不可能会有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是看到妖精了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图书馆的金色妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一个寂寞难耐的留学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑色死神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的孩子和妖精交上朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后灵魂会被带走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生的地方 也有这样的传说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到的是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做维多利加的那个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.98,0:17:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是不存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.33,0:17:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说 你到底把黑色便士藏到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要告诉我 你把它送给你的妖精朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…不是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没空去听小孩子的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点给我交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的…她真的存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的…朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就没有什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在你手上还会在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我手上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我从久城身边滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.59,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾薇…儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 比起这些 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.28,0:19:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来确实是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.87,0:19:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你来救我时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你错看成黑发王子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子  久城是王子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张邮票是给你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你长大成人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用它来成为一个出色的女冒险家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献给我亲爱的孙女艾薇儿 爷爷上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和我做朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你喜欢怪谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你是怎么知道仓库的幽灵是真正的艾薇儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二代奎亚那利用了在学校广为流传的怪谈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把书藏在图书馆也是为个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也会利用仓库怪谈的伎俩来隐藏真正的艾薇儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你个人情 再多告诉你件事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你饱受其害的怪谈 随春而来的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个死神其实是马克·希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是第一代奎亚那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一到春天 就会返回学园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且每次都会招致不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括在紫罗兰色中死去的米莉·玛露
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所藏起来的宝物也会逐一被找到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你果然是真实存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好失礼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我跑来的时候你的确不在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那时你到底在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不认识她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有陌生的家伙来这里了 所以我就藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来了？ 藏在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来藏在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有陌生人来的时候 总会藏在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次来时你没有藏起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸通红通红的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 真的很红
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没红啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.26,0:21:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说没红就是没红
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说她知晓世上万物之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为困扰者指明方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为回报 要求以灵魂为代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.61,0:22:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且将其吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她仅仅是希望能和对方在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信着她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并无永远的分别 一定存在着仅属于自己的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会与这个灵魂邂逅…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.19,0:22:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有此日…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.45,0:24:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 维多利加你鼓着脸 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是因为嘴里塞满了杏仁饼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.29,0:24:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我要和你绝交
